data.title: Daniel Strickland
data.content: Couldn't have a trip to Sydney without visiting my dear friend @thecupcakeprincess_sydney . Long time between cupcakes. Kids loving them and the cookies. For my Sydney friends drop by and taste these awesome cupcakes yourself at 48a Albion Street Waverley. #cupcakes #cakes #waverley #randwick #clovelly Thanks Carissa. #newselfwales
